{"tid":1557341,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解重要搭黨鐵？","createTime":"2019-09-10T05:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T06:56:18.000Z","uid":142252,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"334e2be7177ff4cb48a8a92dd08010e97f365c7c","tid":1557341,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"跳閘有班廢老多管閒事，又要送錢比黨錢。<br />\n相反，你罷搭佢收入直接減少。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接罷搭 不用跳閘不用承受風險</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷搭影響較大，就好似罷買罷食咁簡單。<br />\nFor example, 富臨咁，要改名做生意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又好似啲藍絲酒樓餐廳咁，呢排新聞都話冇人訂枱生意差。黃絲餐廳我唔敢話生意好，但起碼都有條人龍有人食吖<br />\n講真，有咩地方除咗港鐵係去唔到？所有野都係心態決定。有決心就罷到！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">預多少少時間或者行多幾步！身體力行罷搭黨鐵！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重有，唔好再係港鐵站商店/商場買嘢！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利伸 已經一個月有多冇搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f698fbab04db094bcdde6de5d5bec642b9e425e","tid":1557341,"uid":221336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後全部人同我推文個時加埋新屋嶺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以俾呢件事spin走！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如: <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831<br />\n新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7e2769a2b610c4a744a32d3fdfafe5e92bd561dd","tid":1557341,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"自推20連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c71471bca52f5957edeaa988696e2d9731a042","tid":1557341,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"1/20 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知開咩台好"},{"pid":"ca998e7bbe21dea8a6efe24632cd48e362c0ea44","tid":1557341,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"2/20<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推推推"},{"pid":"6479cda5b76025b8e3863b06f286cde905fecfe2","tid":1557341,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"第3連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad16fb5eeccf8a949ee115990c26826fbbe3d38","tid":1557341,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想你地比廢老蝦"},{"pid":"2c32271e3f263ae50a1f35b4cf983229cd60696e","tid":1557341,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6a914913838d3727039852751689f883f67d01","tid":1557341,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-1